title: Sportscene - 24th August 2014 - 720p X264
description:
Sportscene
Sunday 24th August 2014 

Jonathan Sutherland introduces highlights of all the matches in the SPFL Premiership. A confident Celtic side travel to Inverness knowing that they have won three-quarters of all the league clashes between the two teams. Ross County face a Dundee United side buoyed by their opening day victory over Aberdeen, while the Dons take on St Johnstone in Perth and Motherwell experience the new artificial pitch at Kilmarnock. This is the last Sportscene I'll be doing.
